00:06:01.600 --> 00:06:07.600
Inclusive design is a design approach that 
takes as many individuals, their background,

00:06:07.600 --> 00:06:14.480
their needs, experience and ability into account 
from day one of the project. Accessibility is a

00:06:14.480 --> 00:06:20.240
part of inclusive design. We want as many people 
as possible to be able to use our products.

